  28:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                       ##### TIMER Extended features #####
  29:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  30:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   [..]
