1784:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** /**
1785:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief  Configure the TIM commutation event sequence.
1786:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note  This function is mandatory to use the commutation event in order to
1787:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        update the configuration at each commutation detection on the TRGI input of the Timer,
